.TH BEAVER 1 "February 2026" "Beaver" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
beaver \- Beaver command hub and help
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B beaver
.br
.B beaver help
.RI [ topic ]
.br
.B beaver version
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B beaver
is a small command hub for the Beaver environment. It prints an overview
of installed tools and provides topic-specific help.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.BR "(no arguments)"
Show the main help overview and installed tool list.
.TP
.BR help " " [topic]
Show help for a topic. Available topics:
.BR ai ,
.BR internet ,
.BR mail ,
.BR social .
.TP
.B version
Show component versions (delegates to
.BR beaver-version ).
.SH TOPICS
.TP
.B ai
Help for the Beaver AI client.
.TP
.B internet
Help for text-based web browsing.
.TP
.B mail
Help for mail sync and clients.
.TP
.B social
Help for social client usage.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/beaver/ai.env
Configuration for the AI client (if installed).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR beaver-help (1)
.SH AUTHORS
Beaver project.
